  "caption": "Long contexts aren't free. Your LLM forgets things in the middle.The \"Lost in the Middle\" effect shows LLMs struggle to recall info from the middle of long contexts.Place critical instructions and data at the beginning or end of your prompt for better performance.Save this before your next AI build.Written by Kai.Follow @byteflowlabs for AI systems, no hype.",
